Speaking about this, a question arises and I believe it is already asked up in the chat. In KerosineDenominator::denominator you are subtracting the Kerosine's MAINNET_OWNER balance from the Kerosine's totalSupply and you mentioned it is not a great solution. Why is that? (edited)
ehjc 04/19/2024 10:59
Ideally, you’d have an on-chain solution to get the circulating supply (different than balanceOf), which we use to determine the deterministic Kerosene price. However, we found so far no convincing solution for that purpose. Therefore, this approach was chosen for now, but it is upgradable. (edited)
